{"tid":172228,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「心事台」「秘密台」每個人都有秘密，錯過，失去，心痛","createTime":"2017-03-25T18:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T14:17:43.000Z","uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7497cd9772aabda7567e681b39a1522a57541ef6","tid":172228,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:57:50.000Z","msg":"明明好鍾意一個人，但係咩都唔夠膽做，最後睇住佢拍拖，同其他男人游山玩水。<br />\n除非你直接拒絕我，否則個種美好形象深深印入我心中，唔會咁易消失。<br />\n<br />\n時間會沖淡，不。只要在街偶遇到一次，時光就會追溯翻出來，好想好想回到起點，打扮好自己，再次係你面前認識你，了解你，而不是一段成為看到對方都再沒打招呼的一些陌生人。<br />\n<br />\n其他女人根本比唔上你，你知到有男女朋友既界限，但好無奈上天要我頂住頂住，我可以做啲咩？無<br />\n<br />\n人生只有一次，沒頭沒尾的人生，要是沒有你，就像失去了靈魂的軀殼，一變呼喊著，一邊漸漸行屍走肉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者身體基因同內在的自我不配合就會成為人生的輸家。<br />\n<br />\n人無可能強迫另一個人喜歡他。<br />\n點解我依刻個心咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73a98aa5aaea5dceb763c5cf9629f4ea1a0b7e0","tid":172228,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T19:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b152e1ebf2d7abdb7a1b9726aa1ac2e1af7a0d4f","tid":172228,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T19:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1979655a8058033d22221ed5798e0f1788ba00ae","tid":172228,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T19:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07cdd4657283897085e44d04a07735519933169","tid":172228,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T19:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf58ca4a0e38a464b0ffcc9d9a5ed23210393c7","tid":172228,"uid":5205,"